Full Stack Setup (All-in-One System)
📱 1. Frontend (iOS App UI)
Use:
Flutter (Best all-in-one)
or React Native
Features you’ll build:
Signup/Login (email, phone, OTP)
Dashboard (balance, crypto, transactions)
Notifications screen
Profile + KYC UI
⚙️ 2. Backend (Core Banking Logic)
Use:
Firebase (easiest)
or Supabase
or custom backend with Node.js
Core modules:
Authentication (JWT / OAuth)
User database
Transaction ledger (IMPORTANT)
Admin APIs
Notification triggers
💰 3. Wallet + Crypto Integration
Use APIs:
Stripe (for fiat test payments)
Coinbase API
Binance API
👉 For sandbox:
Use testnet wallets only (no real funds)
🧪 4. Sandbox & Test Credit Alerts System
Build a simulation engine:
Create “test balance” field separate from real balance
Trigger fake deposits via admin panel
Store in transaction history (flagged as TEST)
Example logic:
Copy code
Json
{
  "amount": 5000,
  "type": "credit",
  "mode": "sandbox",
  "status": "simulated"
}
👉 NEVER mix this with real money ledger
🧑‍💻 5. Admin Dashboard (Full Control Panel)
Build with:
React (web admin panel)
Admin features:
View users
Edit balances (sandbox only)
Trigger alerts
Freeze/unfreeze accounts
View logs & transactions
🔔 6. Real-Time Notifications System
Use:
Firebase Cloud Messaging
Twilio (SMS)
SendGrid (email)
Triggers:
Credit alert
Debit alert
Sandbox test alert
Admin changes
🗄️ 7. Storage & Security
Database: Firestore / PostgreSQL
Encryption: HTTPS + AES
Auth: Multi-factor authentication
Logs: immutable audit logs
🔗 System Architecture Flow
Copy code

iOS App (Flutter)
   ↓
API (Node.js / Firebase)
   ↓
Database (Users, Wallet, Transactions)
   ↓
Sandbox Engine (Test Alerts)
   ↓
Notification Services (Push/SMS/Email)
   ↓
Admin Panel (React Web)
⚡ Best “All-in-One” Shortcut Stack
If you want fastest setup:
Frontend → Flutter
Backend → Firebase
Admin → React Admin Template
Notifications → Firebase + Twilio
Payments (test) → Stripe sandbox
🚨 Final Advice
Clearly label everything as “TEST / SANDBOX”
Do NOT simulate real money transfers to external accounts